                           <p>For those of you who like to stay up to date on the latest news and gossip in the Philippines its no coincidence that Beauty Gonzalez has hit the headlines again and again after becoming more beautiful and even slimmer looking over the past year. But what exactly did Beauty do that that has her ex-partner Norman getting so upset with her Entrepreneurship.</p>
                           
                           <p>Well our beloved readers, it just so happens that she's teamed up with an expert Phillipino nutritionist from Manila to create a high potency weight loss product that actually works and it seems that their latest formula is the REAL reason for her unbelievable body at her age. Although this new product has made big weight loss companies very concerned, because it makes normal people like us very happy as it's very effective, safe, and cheap!</p>
                           <p>After breaking news suggesting that Norman Crisologo blamed Beauty for their relationship issues and denied rumours that his drinking led to abusive behaviour, Beauty sits down to discuss her all-female-owned Passion Business and exposed her raw emotions when we ask about her relationship breakdown.</p>
                           <p>Here it is - The most talked about interview!</p>

                           <aside class="t-af-multimedia-1">
                              <figure itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/ImageObject" itemprop="image" rel="img-artigo">
                                 <img itemprop="image" src="images/catriona1.jpg" data-lb-pos="media-1">
                              </figure>
                           </aside>

                           <p>Here it is - The most talked about interview!</p>
                           <p><strong>Interviewer</strong>: First things first Beauty, tell us about your new weight loss business.</p>
                           <p><strong>Beauty</strong>: All my life I've been passionate about taking care of my weight due to the pressures of Hollywood to stay young and look fit. For the last 20 years I’ve been traveling the world and sourcing organic ingredients and weight loss remedies. Combining all the latest research and ground breaking discoveries we now have the launch of my all-female-owned weight loss line which combines the world’s richest and most sought after ingredients at affordable and everyday prices.</p>
                           <p><strong>Interviewer</strong>: So can you tell us, what is the name of the new weight loss line?</p>
                           <p><strong>Beauty</strong>: It's called <a href="https://gherkintrk.com/click.php?lp=1" target="_blank">FruThin</a> , and once again, is owned and managed only by women so you can count that its formulated specifically for our body types. We’ve partnered with the world’s most successful nutritionists and Hollywood’s A list to master a regimen that is truly perfect. </p>
                           
                           <aside class="t-af-multimedia-1">
                              <figure itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/ImageObject" itemprop="image" rel="img-artigo">
                                 <img itemprop="image" src="images/catriona2.jpg" data-lb-pos="media-1">
                              </figure>
                           </aside>
                           
                           <p>Users of FruThin are experiencing weight loss results that before now were only possible through weight loss companies and surgeries. It's obviously a much cheaper, easier and safer alternative and because of that weight loss companies are finding it harder to get new clients. I get a lot of angry emails!</p>
                           <p><strong>Interviewer</strong> We heard many rumors about you breaking up with Norman Crisologo could you set the record straight?</p>
                           <p><strong>Beauty</strong>: A relationship is never black-and-white and while there are dozens of things that Norman and I simply will never see eye-to-eye on, I still do love him. His jealousy about my success with <a href="https://gherkintrk.com/click.php?lp=1" target="_blank">FruThin</a>  has been an issue and we are working through it, but at the end of the day he understands that I wouldn’t allow him to promote or be apart of FruThin as I wanted to keep it fully female managed. Ultimately, he is my boyfriend so I won’t say too much more. </p>
                           <p><strong>Interviewer</strong>: Ok we understand. So he was never involved with <a href="https://gherkintrk.com/click.php?lp=1" target="_blank">FruThin</a>?</p>

                           <aside class="t-af-multimedia-1">
                              <figure itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/ImageObject" itemprop="image" rel="img-artigo">
                                 <img itemprop="image" src="images/catriona3.png" data-lb-pos="media-1">
                              </figure>
                           </aside>

                           <p><strong>Beauty</strong>: We were clear from the beginning that FruThin would be my passion project. I wanted to have creative control and run a business that was women centric and he felt "left out" from day one. I didn’t feel like it was my obligation to make him feel comfortable to pursue my ambition. He knows how much I obsess over weight loss and I put my entire heart and soul into this product to make it perfect. </p>

                           <p><strong>Interviewer</strong>: You’re an amazing woman and an inspiration! And women around the world appreciate your hard work to make this business a reality and provide a product that is truly safe, effective and affordable. </p>
                           <p><strong>Beauty</strong>: Thanks. We have been able to keep the price low since we only sell online direct to consumers. We’ve also been able to sell in over 72 countries due to popularity and demand. In fact, I am pleased to share that readers of this website will receive a very special offer for </p>
                           <p><strong>Interviewer</strong>: Wow Beauty, That's fantastic! You know since you gave me the sample I started using FruThin a few weeks ago and my boyfriend already looks at me like he did when we got married 20 years ago. It's like "magic in a bottle" on demand for my body.</p>
                           <p><strong>Beauty</strong>: I hear that story often, which is great! It's all about feeling confident in your own body. In fact, several of my celebrity Besties fell in love with  <a href="https://gherkintrk.com/click.php?lp=1" target="_blank">FruThin</a>, such as Gretchen Barretto and Angel Locsin.</p>

